:

1. *Razmisli* malo o tome šta te čeka. (Think a little about what awaits you.)
2. O čemu *razmišljaš*? (What are you thinking about?)
3. Kada se *razmisli*, to nije tako teško. (When you think about it, it's not that hard.)
4. *Razmislite* o svojim mogućnostima. (Think about your options.)
5. Nisam *razmišljao* o tome. (I hadn't thought about that.)